title: Downtown Luxury Apartment Complex
description: A stunning 15-story mixed-use development featuring 120 luxury apartments with rooftop gardens, fitness facilities, and ground-floor retail spaces. Modern architecture with sustainable building practices.

title: Suburban Family Community Development
description: Large-scale residential community with 50 single-family homes featuring modern architecture, community gardens, and shared recreational facilities. Designed with families in mind.

title: Historic Downtown Renovation
description: Complete restoration of 1920s historic building into modern office spaces and creative studios. Preserved original architectural details while adding contemporary amenities and green infrastructure.

title: Waterfront Resort and Spa
description: Luxury 200-room beachfront resort with spa, multiple restaurants, and water sports facilities. Premium finishes throughout with ocean-view suites and infinity pools.

title: Tech Hub Office Campus
description: State-of-the-art office campus for tech companies featuring collaborative workspaces, innovation labs, and sustainability-focused design. LEED Gold certified.
